_olex2_refinement_description
;
1. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All C(H) groups, All C(H,H) groups, All N(H,H,H) groups
2. Restrained distances
 N1-C20 \\sim C20-C19 \\sim C18-C19
 with sigma of 0.01
3. Uiso/Uaniso restraints and constraints
Uanis(N1) \\sim Ueq, Uanis(C20) \\sim Ueq: with sigma of 0.01 and sigma for
terminal atoms of 0.02
4. Others
 Fixed Sof: I2(0.5) I3(0.5)
5.a Secondary CH2 refined with riding coordinates:
 C17(H17A,H17B), C18(H18A,H18B), C19(H19A,H19B), C20(H20A,H20B)
5.b Aromatic/amide H refined with riding coordinates:
 C2(H2), C3(H3), C5(H5), C6(H6), C8(H8), C9(H9), C10(H10), C12(H12), C13(H13)
5.c Idealised Me refined as rotating group:
 N1(H1A,H1B,H1C)
;
